The in operator

Moreover, the context created by the in operator allows you to use a generator, too.

The example shows how to do it:

def powers_of_2(n):
    power = 1
    for i in range(n):
        yield power
        power *= 2
 
 
for i in range(20):
    if i in powers_of_2(4):
        print(i)


